condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section I.A.1 | Description :The Borrower, acting through its Ministry of Agriculture shall operateand maintain a unit within AGRO RURAL, responsible for the overall coordination and management of the Project | Frequency :Monthly

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section I.A.2 | Description :The Ministry of Agriculture shall establish within ninety (90) daysafter the Effective Date and maintain a Project Steering Committee (Consejo Directivo), to be responsible for providing policyoversight and guidance for Project implementation. | Due Date :20-Mar-2014

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section I.C | Description :AGRO RURAL, shall adopt within ninety (90) days after the Effective Dateand thereafter implement the Project in accordance with a (revised) Operations Manual acceptable to the Bank. | Due Date:20-Mar-2014

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section II. B.1 | Description :AGRO RURAL shall install, within ninety (90) days after theEffective Date, the financial information system (“SIGER”) in the Project coordination office. | Due Date :20-Mar-2014
Finance Agreement :Section 5.01 | Description :MARENASS Regulation duly upated prior to effectiveness | Due Date :30-Oct-2007
